divs: Sighting DetailsWalking to the store off along Research Blvd (10710 Research Blvd, @ about 8:30 pm. I looked up and saw an orange sphere crossing the sky and then watched as either four or five more came into view, creating the effect of a string of pearls, only they looked like basketballs. I do live in an area where there are military bases not to distant from Austin, TX. My overall reaction was curiosity wondering if they could be flairs? I continued on the store.
